        <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/"><img width="46" height="46" alt="Bootstrap" title="Bootstrap" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/bootstrap/bootstrap-original.svg"/></a>
