    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        Consuming way too much media of all kinds: Manga, Comics, Video Games, Books, Movies, Shows...
    </p>
    <p>
        I'm currently preparing the development of a project to backlog all this media consumption into a centralized app, 
        replacing my current stack of trackers that are often specialized in one media type.
    </p>
</Layout>

<style>

    /* small */
    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
        margin bottom:;
    }

    /* socials div */
    .socials {
        margin-top: 1%;
    }
	.socials img:hover {
		transform: scale(1.1);
	}

    /* Button */
    button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #584966;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #1e1e2e;
        font: 600 16px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }
    
    button:hover {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3  ;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

	.link-images img:hover {
		transform: scale(1.3);
	}

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }
</style>
